#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:4
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:6
msgid ""
"An Armature in Blender can be thought of as similar to the armature of a real "
"skeleton, and just like a real skeleton an Armature can consist of many "
"bones. These bones can be moved around and anything that they are attached to "
"or associated with will move and deform in a similar way."
msgstr ""
"Blender 中的骨架就像一个真实的骨架那样，骨架是由许多骨骼组成。这些骨骼可以控制"
"表面附着网格或者相关联的任何东西一起旋转移动。"

#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:11
msgid ""
"An \"armature\" is a type of object used for rigging. A rig is the controls "
"and strings that move a marionette (puppet). Armature object borrows many "
"ideas from real-world skeletons."
msgstr ""
"\"骨架(armature)\"是用于绑定用的，而绑定相当于木偶（傀儡）的控制器和牵线来控制"
"网格物体的变形。同时它还借鉴了真实骨架的许多特点。"

#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:17
msgid "Your First Armature"
msgstr "你的第一个骨架"

#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:19
msgid ""
"In order to see what we are talking about, let us try to add the default "
"armature in Blender."
msgstr "为了看看我们在谈论什么，让我们尝试在Blender中添加默认的骨架。"

#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:21
msgid ""
"(Note that armature editing details are explained in the :doc:`armatures "
"editing section </animation/armatures/bones/editing/index>`.)"
msgstr ""
"(需要注意的是骨架的编辑细节已经在 :doc:`骨架编辑部分 </animation/armatures/"
"bones/editing/index>`。)"

#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:24
msgid "Open a default scene, then:"
msgstr "打开默认的场景, 然后："

#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:26
msgid "Delete all objects in the scene."
msgstr "删除场景中的所有物体。"

#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:27
msgid "Make sure the cursor is in the world origin with :kbd:`Shift-C`."
msgstr "按下键盘  :kbd:`Shift-C` 确保3D游标在世界的原点。"

#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:28
msgid "Press :kbd:`Numpad1` to see the world in Front view."
msgstr "按数字键盘上的 :kbd:`Numpad1` 键切换到前视图。"

#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:29
msgid "Add a *Single Bone* (:menuselection:`Add --> Armature`)."
msgstr "添加一个 *骨骼*  (:menuselection:`添加 --> 骨架`)."

#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:30
msgid "Press :kbd:`NumpadDelete` to see the armature at maximum zoom."
msgstr "按 :kbd:`NumpadDelete` 视图最大化查看骨架。"

#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:34
msgid "The default armature."
msgstr "默认骨架。"

#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:38
msgid "The Armature Object"
msgstr "骨架物体"

#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:40
msgid "As you can see, an armature is like any other object type in Blender:"
msgstr "正如你所看到的, 骨架物体像Blender 的其它物体类型:"

#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:42
msgid "It has an origin, a position, a rotation and a scale factor."
msgstr "它有一个原心，还有位置、 旋转和缩放系数。"

#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:43
msgid "It has an Object Data data-block, that can be edited in *Edit Mode*."
msgstr "有物体数据块, 所以能够在 *编辑模式* 中被编辑."

#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:44
msgid ""
"It can be linked to other scenes, and the same armature data can be reused on "
"multiple objects."
msgstr "它可以被连结到其它场景, 同样的骨架数据可以被多个物体使用。"

#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:45
msgid ""
"All animation you do in *Object Mode* is only working on the whole object, "
"not the armature's bones (use the *Pose Mode* to do this)."
msgstr ""
"在 *物体模式* 下所有的动画仅仅工作在整个物体的，而不是骨架的骨骼 (在 *姿态模式"
"下* 可以做到这点)。"

#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:48
msgid ""
"As armatures are designed to be posed, either for a static or animated scene, "
"they have a specific state, called \"rest position\". This is the armature's "
"default \"shape\", the default position/rotation/scale of its bones, as set "
"in *Edit Mode*."
msgstr ""
"骨架是为姿势设计的, 无论是静态或动态场景, 它们有一个特别的姿态叫 “重置位置"
"（rest position）”。 这个骨骼有默认的“形状”, 默认的位置/旋转/缩放, 在 *编辑模"
"式* 可以设置改变它们。"

#: ../../manual/animation/armatures/introduction.rst:52
msgid ""
"In *Edit Mode*, you will always see your armature in rest position, whereas "
"in *Object Mode* and *Pose Mode*, you usually get the current \"pose\" of the "
"armature (unless you enable the *Rest Position* button of the *Armature* "
"panel)."
msgstr ""
"在 *编辑模式*， 你总是看到骨架处于重置位置（rest position）, 而在 *物体模式* "
"和 *姿态模式*, 你一般看到的是当前的骨架“姿势”(除非你启用了 *骨架（Armature）* "
"面板的 *重置位置（rest position）* 按钮把它恢复到初始姿势)。"
